WEBVTT

1
01:30:54.800 --> 01:30:56.120 
银行不同意吗
Bank said no?

2
01:30:56.120 --> 01:30:57.410 
坚决不同意
Emphatically.

3
01:30:57.410 --> 01:30:58.880 
每一家都是
Repeatedly.

4
01:30:59.860 --> 01:31:02.840 
我觉得国内已经没有银行家可以让我忽悠
I don't think there's a banker left in the country I can fool into

5
01:31:02.840 --> 01:31:04.880 
借给我更多钱了 所以
loaning me more money, so...

6
01:31:07.910 --> 01:31:09.820 
我很抱歉让你们所有人失望了
I'm really sorry to disappoint you all.

7
01:31:09.820 --> 01:31:11.000 
别担心 Barnum
Don't worry, Barnum.

8
01:31:11.000 --> 01:31:13.000 
现在我们早就习惯了
We've gotten used to it by now.

